msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Enter each restriction of one hypothesis on a new line,\n"
"e.g., Low <= Mid <= High\n"
"where 'Low'/'Mid'/'High' are the factor level names.\n"
"Click on the 'plus' icon to add more hypotheses. \n"
"Click the information icon for more examples."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie jede Beschränkung einer Hypothese in eine neue Zeile ein,\n"
